reviews.title: Cozy seating, delicious food & drinks at the entrance to Epe
reviews.text:
It is a beautiful, warm late summer evening on this September 15th. Spontaneously ended up at VanOuds. The terrace is pleasantly filled. The location is beautiful, just at the northern entrance to the center of Epe. Remarkably friendly service. Dishes from the kitchen are delicious.
Great night!!!
